Paper locator
=============

http://david-peter.de/pl

Paper locator is an easy and universal way to retrieve scientific papers from a given reference or citation.

It automates the process of extracting journal, issue and page from the text and searching the journal website manually by redirecting you to the correct page immediately.

- Paste a piece of text containing a reference
- Press enter or click one of the buttons


Try one of the following:
  [1] R. B. Laughlin, Phys. Rev. Lett. 50, 1395 (1983).
  prl 17 1133
  arXiv:quant-ph/9707021
  lained in Nature Physics 1, 23 by Imm

